# DesiDevloper.com — Cursor Project Rules v3.0

## Stack
- Pure HTML5 + CSS3 + Vanilla JavaScript ONLY
- NO React, Vue, Svelte, Angular, or any JS framework
- NO Tailwind, Bootstrap, or any CSS framework
- NO npm packages for frontend — Node.js only for build scripts
- Hosted on Hostinger Business (shared hosting — no server-side code)

## Brand Colors
- Primary:    #1E40AF  (blue)
- Accent:     #F59E0B  (amber/gold)
- Text:       #111827  (near-black)
- Background: #FFFFFF  (white)
- WhatsApp:   #25D366  (green)
- LinkedIn:   #0A66C2  (blue)

## Architecture
- ALL service pages: /services/[slug].html
- Template: /services/service-template.html
- Data file: /data/services-data.json
- Generator: /scripts/generate-pages.js
- Nav and footer: injected at BUILD TIME

## Every Service Page: 13 Sections
1. Navigation
2. Hero
3. Problem
4. Solution
5. Process
6. Timeline
7. What's Included
8. Portfolio
9. Related Services
10. Social Proof
11. Mini Case Study
12. FAQ
13. Final CTA + Footer
